        "rich_text_pVwLmi": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Since you were a little girl, you have always dreamt of this big day. Now that your wedding day is getting closer, your gallery is overflowing with inspiration photos. Your Pinterest is filled with wedding moodboards; friends and family are sending you aesthetic reels that feel too good to come true! It is all overwhelming and exciting all at once, but the question is: what kind of wedding jewellery should you buy?</p><p>An Indian wedding, after all, is not just an event but a lifelong dream of both the bride and the parents. It is a festival of emotions, the dhols beating, the fragrance of marigold, the rush of colors, and the sound of pure joy. Gold carries the tradition of this auspicious beginning of partners, while platinum promises forever. We have curated jewelry ideas for the modern bride who doesn’t wear jewelry only for the big day and then preserve it in the safe until it has to be passed on. For the modern bride, we craft diamond jewellery that stays on forever with the same sparkle as the one on your wedding day.<br/><br/></p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_xLCWVU": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Haldi Jewelry: Jewelry That Radiates The Sunshine Glow",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Haldi Jewelry: Jewelry That Radiates The Sunshine Glow</h2>",
            "custom_id": "haldi"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_n6LzA3": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Haldi.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Welcome the warmth of new beginnings with laughter and joy. With turmeric’s golden hues all around, your jewelry should reflect your sunshine energy. Think delicate gold floral earrings or a diamond pendant that catches the light without overwhelming your look. If you are worried that the turmeric will stain your jewelry, adorn your ears with small but regal diamond <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/stud-earrings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond Stud Earrings\">stud earrings</a> that come in unique designs such as our Evergreen Round Diamond Earrings.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_mUdzM7": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Mehendi Moment: Jewelry That Shines Through Every Shade Of Love",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Mehendi Moment: Jewelry That Shines Through Every Shade Of Love</h2>",
            "custom_id": "mehendi"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_nJaixi": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Mehndi.jpg",
            "text": "<p>As the color of henna deepens, signifying your love, style your mehendi outfit to reflect this forever love. Opt for jewelry that complements your mehendi, not hides it. A sui dhaga earring or layered necklaces look elegant. You can choose a dainty <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/tennis-bracelets\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond Tennis Bracelets\">tennis bracelet</a> lab grown diamonds to add sparkle to your look.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_VgX3Wj": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Sangeet: Jewelry That Keeps You Spotlight Ready",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Sangeet: Jewelry That Keeps You Spotlight Ready</h2>",
            "custom_id": "sangeet"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_yC9UwA": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Sangeet.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Bring shine to all your moves with a diamond jewellery set crafted to show off your dazzling look. On your Sangeet night, show your vibrant self with a diamond <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-necklaces\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Diamond Necklace\">necklace</a> paired with matching diamond earrings as you win his heart all over again under the spotlight. Stack bangles and bracelets on your hands that enhance the grace you bring to the stage. Choose jewelry that is minimal yet elegant - a statement piece that’s comfortable for you to dance the night away.\t\t</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_YEL9Af": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Engagement Ceremony: Jewelry For Your Solitaire Moment ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Engagement Ceremony: Jewelry For Your Solitaire Moment </h2>",
            "custom_id": "engagement"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_kA6rkX": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Engagement_8d33f5bf-0b8b-4aea-928e-3b7d47da1071.jpg",
            "text": "<p>A solitaire engagement ring is on every woman’s wishlist. If you are looking for a diamond <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-ring\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond Engagement Ring\">engagement ring</a> for a bride, lab grown diamonds are perfect to get her a big stone she will be flaunting all the time. There are several cuts, settings, and shanks to choose from, each featuring their own beauty. While selecting, consider the preferable cuts, the most common and classic being a round solitaire ring. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_gHcr6D": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>We understand how exciting yet unnerving engagement ring shopping can be, so we curate simple guide-like blogs for you to select the dream <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/solitaire-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond Solitaire Ring\">solitaire ring</a>.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_3FCJ4y": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Wedding Day: Jewelry That Keeps Its Vows Seriously ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Wedding Day: Jewelry That Keeps Its Vows Seriously </h2>",
            "custom_id": "wedding"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_QJntgY": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Wedding_Day.jpg",
            "text": "<p>The big day is nearing, and every little detail - be it the outfit, the jewelry, or the makeup - needs to be perfect. Diamond bridal sets should complement the outfit and make the bride stand out in the crowd. The most important is the wedding ring. Choose a wedding ring that sits well with the engagement ring when stacked or has the same texture, to be styled on different fingers. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_qLpneD": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>You can even opt for stackable lab grown diamond ring that are designed for the coordinated look of the engagement ring and <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/wedding-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Diamond Wedding Ring\">wedding ring</a>. Style the look with a unique wedding jewellery set for bride or a diamond necklace for bride that is not only perfect for the big day but can be worn as signature pieces daily.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_hRmtTB": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Reception: Jewelry For Your Red Carpet Elegance",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Reception: Jewelry For Your Red Carpet Elegance</h2>",
            "custom_id": "reception"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_HDhA3z": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Reception.jpg",
            "text": "<p>It’s time to be congratulated on your milestone moment. Many congratulatory handshakes, hugs, and pictures will be captured. For this red carpet elegance, bring your look to life with details that elevate your outfit. Adorn your wrist with a diamond <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-bracelets\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Diamond Bracelets\">bracelet</a> that glints at every handshake. Wear a diamond chain that embraces you so perfectly that its shine reflects your smile and enhances the beauty of your collarbones. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_7VWbiQ": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion </h2><p>Weddings are supposed to be grand, portraying your joy and your dreams. Such a special, once-in-a-lifetime moment demands equally elegant accessories that you can wear forever. The jewelry you will choose will remind you of these occasions, whether it is for your joyous sangeet, the laughter during mehendi, or the promises you made on your wedding day. Choose pieces that not only go with the outfit, but also truly feel true to you. </p>",
            "custom_id": "conclusion"
          }
        }
      },
